Company Overview of Virtus Equity Trust - Virtus Mid-Cap Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Virtus Equity Trust - Virtus Mid-Cap Growth Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Investment Advisers, Inc. and Kayne Anderson Rudnick Investment Management, LLC. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth stocks of mid-cap companies having market capitalization within the range of the Russell Midcap Index. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors such as sustainable competitive advantage, strong management and low financial risk, consistently gro...
Virtus Equity Trust - Virtus Mid-Cap Growth Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Investment Advisers, Inc. and Kayne Anderson Rudnick Investment Management, LLC. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth stocks of mid-cap companies having market capitalization within the range of the Russell Midcap Index. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors such as sustainable competitive advantage, strong management and low financial risk, consistently growing, highly profitable, low-debt companies with rising cash flows, company’s strength of management, its relative competitive position in the industry, and its financial structure to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell Midcap Growth Index. The fund employs proprietary research to create its portfolio. It was formerly known as Phoenix Equity Trust - Virtus Mid-Cap Growth Fund. Virtus Equity Trust - Virtus Mid-Cap Growth Fund was formed on December 31, 1975 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


