Virtus Equity Trust Dividend Announcement(NASDAQ:FMIVX)DIVIDEND ANNOUNCEMENT: Virtus Equity Trust (NASDAQ: FMIVX) today declared a dividend of $0.4000 per shareJune 22, 2017Virtus Equity Trust (NASDAQ: FMIVX) today declared a dividend of $ 0.4000 per share payable on June 22, 2017 to shareholders of record as of June 21, 2017. Dividend amount recorded is an increase of $ 0.154 from last dividend Paid.Virtus Equity Trust (NASDAQ:FMIVX) has paid dividends since 2004, has a current dividend yield of 2.3% and has increased its dividends for 1 successive years.The stock price closed yesterday at $ 35.18 and has a 52 week low/high of $ 31.45 and $ 39.01. For more information on Virtus Equity Trust click here.Virtus Equity Trust current dividend information as per the date of this press release is:Dividend Declaration Date: June 22, 2017Dividend Ex Date: June 22, 2017Dividend Record Date: June 21, 2017Dividend Payment Date: June 22, 2017Dividend Amount: $ 0.4000


